    "Moreover, the study seeks to map the distribution and significance of scholarly journals publishing GeoGebra research, thereby identifying the leading periodicals in the field.",
    "To achieve these objectives, this research endeavours to answer the following questions:",
    "• What are the publication trends of GeoGebra research in mathematics education from 2007 to 2023?",
    "• How has the conceptual space and structure of the scholarly network surrounding GeoGebra research evolved from 2007 to 2023 based on an analysis of keyword frequencies and co-occurrences in published literature?",
    "• What are the major thematic clusters in GeoGebra research, and how do they contribute to the field of mathematics education?"
